commits.message: Hack to make google maps work
Cut out start of path and minor fixes
Add firebase to communicate with turn signal
Add hash set for storing visited intersections
Feedback for driver on scan left/right + adjustments to interpolation to account for frequent intersections
Fix menu trigger for camera (2 way toggle now)
Make camera run in the background
Clean up and add demoRoute visualization
Detect if eyes are closed and warn user with text to speech if they are.
Route to destination using google maps API and also hardcoded demoRoute
Added getter methods for getting the time from the last time the user turned left/right or stayed center (face).
